testcase.name: The Minefield object should do stuff
toCharList should return a list of chars
or *
createFieldItems should without mines when return a field item when one is entered
createFieldItems should without mines when return two field items when two are entered
createFieldItems should without mines when return field item List for 1 row with correct coordinates
createFieldItems should without mines when return field item List for 2 rows with correct coordinates
createFieldItems should without mines when return field item List for 3 rows with correct coordinates
createFieldItems should without mines when return field item List for 4 rows with correct coordinates
createFieldItems should with mines when return with isMine false when no mine is entered
createFieldItems should with mines when return with isMine true when * is entered
createFieldItems should with mines when return with isMine true when * is entered as second item
createFieldItems should with mines when return with isMine true when * is entered in second row
createFieldItems should with mines when return with isMine true when * is entered in third row
createFieldItems should with mines when return with isMine true when * is entered in fourth row
createFieldItems should with mines when return with isMine true when * is entered in 3,4 row
getFieldsToIncrement should return correct fields to increment for one row location 1,1
getFieldsToIncrement should return correct fields to increment for one row location 1,2
getFieldsToIncrement should return correct fields to increment for one row 1,3
getFieldsToIncrement should return correct fields to increment for one row location 1,4
getFieldsToIncrement should return correct fields to increment for two rows location 2,1
getFieldsToIncrement should return correct fields to increment for two rows location 2,3
getFieldsToIncrement should return correct fields to increment for three rows location 3,1
getFieldsToIncrement should return correct fields to increment for four rows location 4,2
getFieldsToIncrement should return correct fields to increment for four rows where bomb is in the middle
incrementMinefield should increment fieldItems for one rowz
